import { AppBar, Container, Typography, Select, Toolbar, MenuItem} from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar color="transparent" position="static">
      <Container>
        <Toolbar>
          <Typography>Bitcoin Today</Typography>
            <Select variant="outlined" style={{width:100,height:40}} >
            <MenuItem>USD</MenuItem>
            <MenuItem>EUR</MenuItem>
           </Select>
          </Toolbar>
        </Container>
      </AppBar>
  )
}

export default Header
